Alang-alang, saya nak sebut yang semalam…

231
00:21:45,304 --> 00:21:48,265
<i>Dia mungkin nak mengelak aku. Aku faham.</i>

232
00:21:48,765 --> 00:21:51,685
- Untunglah, kerja kita makin bertimbun.
- Itulah.

233
00:21:51,768 --> 00:21:54,688
Kasihan Park Kyeong-Nam.
Awak dahlah banyak kerja.

234
00:21:54,771 --> 00:21:55,605
Betul.

235
00:21:55,689 --> 00:21:58,233
Anggaplah itu rezeki.
Fokus satu-satu dulu.

236
00:21:58,317 --> 00:22:01,361
Tapi awak okey tak?
Kerja promosi macam berat saja.

237
00:22:01,445 --> 00:22:04,281
Ya. Sebab itu awak patut tolong.

238
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:05,949
Boleh saja.

239
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:11,121
<i>Kami bukan satu pasukan,</i>
<i>jadi ini tak pelik pun.</i>

240
00:22:11,204 --> 00:22:12,998
<i>Yalah, dia Park Kyeong-nam.</i>

241
00:22:13,081 --> 00:22:13,915
Oh, ya.

242
00:22:19,129 --> 00:22:20,964
Kita sambung di sana nanti.

243
00:22:21,048 --> 00:22:22,049
Okey.

244
00:22:22,132 --> 00:22:25,052
- Saya nak minum <i>makgeolli</i>.
- Saya tak minum arak.

245
00:22:25,135 --> 00:22:27,304
- Eh, tak bolehlah begitu.
- Jomlah.

246
00:22:27,387 --> 00:22:29,222
- Marilah minum.
- Alamak.

247
00:22:29,306 --> 00:22:30,307
Awak bosanlah.

248
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:33,518
Tunggu sekejap.

249
00:22:34,353 --> 00:22:36,021
Kenapa aku yang mengelak?

250
00:22:50,285 --> 00:22:53,372
Tak bolehkah kita keluar makan esok?
Malam ini sejuk.

251
00:22:54,623 --> 00:22:58,293
Saya sampai 30 minit lagi.
Tunggu. Saya tersalah belok.

252
00:22:58,377 --> 00:23:01,380
Hei, janganlah… Berilah jalan…

253
00:23:01,963 --> 00:23:03,173
Jahatnya.

254
00:23:03,256 --> 00:23:04,091
PEMANDU BARU

255
00:23:04,174 --> 00:23:05,342
Berilah jalan!

256
00:23:08,595 --> 00:23:10,347
Saya tunggu awak di kafe.

257
00:23:13,725 --> 00:23:15,018
Hai, Seo Mi-rae.

258
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:17,771
Helo. Awak buat apa di sini?

259
00:23:17,854 --> 00:23:20,065
Saya ada mesyuarat dengan Kyeong-nam.

260
00:23:23,402 --> 00:23:25,153
Latte dah siap.

261
00:23:26,238 --> 00:23:27,322
Kacau betullah.

262
00:23:29,741 --> 00:23:32,411
<i>Ya. Betullah macam Park Kyeong-nam cakap.</i>

263
00:23:32,494 --> 00:23:35,914
<i>Bukan aku yang ditolak.</i>
<i>Aku tak perlu terus buat begini.</i>

264
00:23:44,673 --> 00:23:46,007
<i>Kena yakin.</i>

265
00:23:47,676 --> 00:23:49,094
<i>Berdiri tegak.</i>

266
00:23:51,555 --> 00:23:52,722
<i>Senyum.</i>

267
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:57,436
<i>Kenapa? Cantik sangat?</i>

268
00:24:05,235 --> 00:24:06,153
AWAS KACA

269
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:12,576
Awak okey? Kuat betul terhantuk.

270
00:24:14,536 --> 00:24:15,871
Saya okey.

271
00:24:16,455 --> 00:24:18,206
Bunyinya saja yang kuat.

272
00:24:22,377 --> 00:24:25,881
<i>Kecemasan. Bila nak sampai?</i>
<i>Saya nak tunggu di luar.</i>

273
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:30,552
<i>Kenapa? Paling cepat pun, 20 minit lagi.</i>

274
00:24:30,635 --> 00:24:33,305
<i>Di luar sejuklah. Duduk saja di situ.</i>

275
00:24:33,388 --> 00:24:34,723
<i>Nanti saya sampailah.</i>

276
00:24:40,395 --> 00:24:41,354
Awak nak pergi?

277
00:24:42,063 --> 00:24:44,232
Saya cuma nak ke tandas.

278
00:24:48,528 --> 00:24:49,821
Risaulah tengok dia.

279
00:24:56,203 --> 00:24:57,245
Ini apa?

280
00:24:57,954 --> 00:24:59,372
Bila pula benjol?

281
00:25:03,210 --> 00:25:04,794
Apa aku nak buat?

282
00:25:11,968 --> 00:25:12,969
Pergi dulu.

283
00:25:14,054 --> 00:25:15,555
Jangan lupa sapu ubat.

284
00:25:20,185 --> 00:25:21,520
Kalut betullah dia.

285
00:25:21,603 --> 00:25:23,772
Nanti mesti dia terhantuk lagi.

286
00:25:23,855 --> 00:25:25,106
Kita cakap apa tadi?

287
00:25:28,026 --> 00:25:29,027
Tunggu sekejap.

288
00:25:42,958 --> 00:25:43,792
Sama tak?

289
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:53,343
Maaf banyak-banyak.

290
00:25:53,426 --> 00:25:56,972
Saya signal sampai 100 kali
semasa nak datang sini.

291
00:25:57,889 --> 00:25:58,723
Alamak!

292
00:25:58,807 --> 00:25:59,933
Apa dah jadi?

293
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,103
- Awak bergaduh?
- Tak.

294
00:26:03,603 --> 00:26:06,481
- Jomlah kita pergi. Cepat!
- Okey.

295
00:26:07,482 --> 00:26:10,360
Aduh, malu gila saya tadi!

296
00:26:10,443 --> 00:26:12,445
Jalanlah. Cepat.

297
00:26:12,529 --> 00:26:13,363
Okey.

298
00:26:13,446 --> 00:26:14,531
- Jalan!
- Okey.

299
00:26:20,537 --> 00:26:21,371
Nah.

300
00:26:22,414 --> 00:26:23,248
Terima kasih.

301
00:26:27,252 --> 00:26:29,254
Nak gelak, gelaklah kuat-kuat.

302
00:26:33,675 --> 00:26:34,843
Eh, sekejap.

303
00:26:34,926 --> 00:26:37,470
Besarnya benjol awak.
Macam mana awak jalan?

304
00:26:37,554 --> 00:26:40,932
Hei, kalau awak tak pandu kereta
dan lambat sampai…

305
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:42,684
Lupakan saja.

306
00:26:43,393 --> 00:26:47,314
Saya cuma nak tumpangkan
supaya awak selesa sebab hari ini sejuk.

307
00:26:48,982 --> 00:26:51,318
Kenapa awak boleh lepak? Tak pergi dating?

308
00:26:51,401 --> 00:26:52,235
Apa?

309
00:26:55,155 --> 00:26:57,073
Saya nak rehat dulu.

310
00:26:58,908 --> 00:26:59,909
Kenapa?

311
00:27:00,452 --> 00:27:02,871
Entahlah, dating macam buang masa saja.

312
00:27:05,332 --> 00:27:06,791
Kenapa tiru saya?

313
00:27:08,585 --> 00:27:11,421
Penat saya bersolek
dan melaram dari pagi-pagi

314
00:27:11,504 --> 00:27:14,883
untuk berlagak comel
dengan lelaki yang saya tak suka.

315
00:27:14,966 --> 00:27:17,844
Kemudian saya balik,
cuci mekap dan rasa sedih.

316
00:27:17,927 --> 00:27:22,682
Rasa macam sia-sia saja usia muda saya.

317
00:27:22,766 --> 00:27:25,727
Takkanlah ada yang lebih seronok
daripada bercinta,

318
00:27:25,810 --> 00:27:27,562
tapi saya saja tak tahu?

319
00:27:27,646 --> 00:27:30,357
Apa kata awak cuba siasat?

320
00:27:31,858 --> 00:27:35,487
Mustahil, tak ada
yang lebih seronok daripada dating.

321
00:27:36,655 --> 00:27:39,282
Tapi susahnya nak cari lelaki
yang saya suka!

322
00:27:41,159 --> 00:27:43,495
Kalau dah tahu, tak payahlah tanya.

323
00:27:43,995 --> 00:27:48,375
Lebih baik awak fikir tentang benjol awak.
Macam mana awak nak pergi kerja?

324
00:27:58,093 --> 00:28:01,513
Realistik. Realistik sangat.
Orang takkan perasan langsung.

325
00:28:01,596 --> 00:28:02,430
Betulkah?

326
00:28:06,309 --> 00:28:08,978
Saya rasa orang boleh perasan.

327
00:28:09,771 --> 00:28:11,022
Potong teruslah.

328
00:28:12,273 --> 00:28:15,902
Tahu tak, 97% wanita yang potong
rambut depan akan menyesal?

329
00:28:15,985 --> 00:28:19,781
Kalau potong, mesti awak tak sabar
tunggu rambut panjang balik.

330
00:28:19,864 --> 00:28:21,408
Dengarlah nasihat saya.

331
00:28:28,248 --> 00:28:31,334
Awak potong rambut? Cantiknya.

332
00:28:31,418 --> 00:28:33,169
- Lawalah.
- Terima kasih.

333
00:28:33,253 --> 00:28:34,504
Sesuai dengan awak.

334
00:28:34,587 --> 00:28:36,339
- Biar betul!
- Wah.

335
00:28:38,967 --> 00:28:39,801
Apa dah jadi?

336
00:28:40,301 --> 00:28:41,803
Rambut palsukah?

337
00:28:42,637 --> 00:28:43,722
Nampak sangatkah?

338
00:28:43,805 --> 00:28:45,181
Dari dekat, nampaklah.

339
00:28:46,433 --> 00:28:48,643
Kenapa? Awak nak cuba gaya baru?

340
00:28:49,602 --> 00:28:50,437
Apa?

341
00:28:51,813 --> 00:28:53,815
Janganlah salah faham.

342
00:28:53,898 --> 00:28:56,901
Saya saja-saja nak ubah gaya sikit.

343
00:29:10,999 --> 00:29:12,333
Helo.

344
00:29:18,757 --> 00:29:19,841
Apa dah jadi?

345
00:29:20,967 --> 00:29:22,969
Tiba-tiba tukar gaya rambut?

346
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:34,272
Alamak, malunya.

347
00:29:36,983 --> 00:29:37,901
Perempuan gila…

348
00:29:37,984 --> 00:29:41,154
<i>Saya sebenarnya tak nak ungkit hal ini.</i>

349
00:29:41,946 --> 00:29:43,865
- Apa?
- Awak belum lupakan saya?

350
00:29:43,948 --> 00:29:45,533
Perempuan gila!

351
00:29:48,453 --> 00:29:49,287
Cik Yun.

352
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:51,247
- Awak okey?
- Kenapa tanya?

353
00:29:51,331 --> 00:29:55,543
Awak asyik melalak tiba-tiba
beberapa hari ini.

354
00:29:55,627 --> 00:29:57,128
Pelik jugalah.

355
00:29:57,212 --> 00:29:58,046
Apa?

356
00:29:58,129 --> 00:30:00,632
<i>Awak diam-diam tinggalkan snek</i>
<i>di depan bilik saya.</i>

357
00:30:00,715 --> 00:30:02,634
<i>Janganlah begitu. Itu…</i>

358
00:30:02,717 --> 00:30:03,635
<i>Sebenarnya…</i>

359
00:30:03,718 --> 00:30:05,637
- Apa?
- Itu untuk So-yeong!

360
00:30:11,267 --> 00:30:13,728
So-yeong, pergilah. Keluar.

361
00:30:13,812 --> 00:30:15,563
Saya tak larat. Pergi.

362
00:30:15,647 --> 00:30:16,981
Okey.

363
00:30:22,487 --> 00:30:24,405
Biar benar?

364
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:32,080
Aku beri kau 10 minit saja lagi.

365
00:30:45,844 --> 00:30:46,803
Apa?

366
00:30:54,686 --> 00:30:55,937
Sejuknya.

367
00:30:58,523 --> 00:31:01,025
Tolonglah. Jangan buat begini!

368
00:31:04,821 --> 00:31:05,989
<i>30 minit saja lagi.</i>

369
00:31:06,072 --> 00:31:07,991
Biar benar?

370
00:31:08,533 --> 00:31:10,410
Tak habis-habis cakap 30 minit.

371
00:31:18,251 --> 00:31:19,085
Sejuknya!

372
00:31:27,802 --> 00:31:28,636
Aduh…

373
00:31:41,858 --> 00:31:43,276
Saya pun sejuk.

374
00:31:56,039 --> 00:31:57,749
Ini saja pemanas yang ada.

375
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:01,794
Tapi…

376
00:32:04,797 --> 00:32:07,091
Awak kata awak pun sejuk.

377
00:32:07,592 --> 00:32:08,801
Kita kongsilah.

378
00:32:21,439 --> 00:32:23,191
Benjol semalam dah baik?

379
00:32:24,025 --> 00:32:27,028
Dah surut.

380
00:32:30,615 --> 00:32:31,532
Nasib baik.

381
00:32:41,125 --> 00:32:44,796
Dong-min kata lambat juga
kamu balik ke Seoul Ahad lepas.

382
00:32:44,879 --> 00:32:46,714
Mesti kamu berseronok.

383
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:49,884
Ya.

384
00:32:49,968 --> 00:32:52,387
Kami tengok laut, pergi makan-makan.

385
00:32:54,889 --> 00:32:55,723
Kami cuma…

386
00:32:56,516 --> 00:32:57,433
Ya.

387
00:32:58,518 --> 00:33:01,604
Cemburulah saya tengok gambar kamu.

388
00:33:01,688 --> 00:33:06,192
Cik Yun nak balik awal, jadi saya
makan mi segera di lapangan terbang.

389
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:10,154
Maksudnya,

390
00:33:11,364 --> 00:33:12,782
awak tak nak balik awal?

391
00:33:23,751 --> 00:33:24,585
Saya…

392
00:33:25,294 --> 00:33:28,673
Ya, saya nak lepak dulu
dan makan sedap-sedap.

393
00:33:29,966 --> 00:33:32,969
Lain kali, saya pun nak balik lambat.

394
00:33:36,764 --> 00:33:37,765
Okey.

395
00:33:47,775 --> 00:33:48,609
MUAT NAIK SELESAI

396
00:34:23,853 --> 00:34:25,730
Jumpa lagi esok.

397
00:34:26,481 --> 00:34:27,315
Okey.

398
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:07,772
SAYA NAK CAKAP YANG SAYA SUKA AWAK

399
00:36:03,786 --> 00:36:06,789
<i>Saya nak cakap yang saya suka awak.</i>

400
00:36:18,009 --> 00:36:19,510
<i>Dah dapat surat saya?</i>

401
00:36:21,137 --> 00:36:23,389
<i>Aduhai, malunya.</i>

402
00:36:23,472 --> 00:36:24,390
Apa?

403
00:36:24,473 --> 00:36:25,308
<i>Terus terang,</i>

404
00:36:26,684 --> 00:36:28,186
saya bengang dengan awak.

405
00:36:28,895 --> 00:36:31,939
Sebab awak tak jawab pun
semasa saya ajak ikut saya.

406
00:36:33,191 --> 00:36:36,027
Saya ingat saya nak lupakan awak, tapi…

407
00:36:37,236 --> 00:36:38,613
Tapi susah betul.

408
00:36:40,865 --> 00:36:41,949
<i>Saya rindu awak.</i>

409
00:37:24,867 --> 00:37:26,661
1: PlanC
2: DIA YANG PERLU DIKENAL

410
00:37:30,498 --> 00:37:32,833
<i>Selama ini, </i>DYPD <i>dapat nombor satu.</i>

411
00:37:32,917 --> 00:37:35,419
<i>- Sekali dah jatuh, habislah.</i>
<i>- Takziah.</i>

412
00:37:35,503 --> 00:37:38,005
<i>- Dah lama patut jatuh.</i>
<i>- Hwany hebat.</i>

413
00:37:38,089 --> 00:37:40,174
<i>Ini kali pertama dia jatuh, bukan?</i>

414
00:37:41,467 --> 00:37:44,053
<i>Inilah manfaat menang anugerah, bukan?</i>

415
00:37:44,136 --> 00:37:45,388
Jangan seronok dulu.

416
00:37:45,471 --> 00:37:47,974
Sekali-sekala, berilah saya peluang.

417
00:37:48,057 --> 00:37:50,142
Awak lupakah apa jadi di Busan?

418
00:37:50,935 --> 00:37:53,104
<i>Awak buat apa esok? Jom pergi minum.</i>

419
00:37:53,187 --> 00:37:54,105
Awak tak kerja?

420
00:37:54,188 --> 00:37:57,817
Kita kena raikan.
Manalah tahu minggu depan jatuh balik.

421
00:37:59,193 --> 00:38:00,736
Okey, nanti saya beritahu.

422
00:38:14,917 --> 00:38:17,378
- Ya. Saya langsung tak tahu.
- Samalah.

423
00:38:18,379 --> 00:38:19,463
Hei!

424
00:38:19,547 --> 00:38:21,215
- Hai, Mi-rae.
- Hai.

425
00:38:29,181 --> 00:38:30,433
Awak okey?

426
00:38:32,018 --> 00:38:33,519
Ya, saya okey.

427
00:38:34,020 --> 00:38:37,189
Ini hal biasa saja. Jangan risau sangat.

428
00:38:37,273 --> 00:38:38,107
Ya.

429
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:40,359
Mesti <i>DYPD </i>naik balik!

430
00:38:40,443 --> 00:38:41,444
Betul.

431
00:38:41,527 --> 00:38:44,780
Kadang-kadang dia di atas,
kadang-kadang dia jatuh,

432
00:38:44,864 --> 00:38:48,200
tapi kalau penulis awak fokus,
mesti okey, betul tak?

433
00:38:58,127 --> 00:38:58,961
Alamak.

434
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:06,302
Janganlah sedih.
Tak apa. Nak buat macam mana?

435
00:39:06,385 --> 00:39:10,222
<i>PlanC </i>menang anugerah besar
dan dapat liputan meluas.

436
00:39:14,268 --> 00:39:15,186
En. Hwang.

437
00:39:15,269 --> 00:39:16,979
Apa rancangannya sekarang?

438
00:39:18,189 --> 00:39:20,566
- Apa?
- Awak ada rancangan, bukan?

439
00:39:21,984 --> 00:39:24,570
Mestilah. Saya…

440
00:39:24,653 --> 00:39:28,532
Saya akan berusaha dengan Cik Yun
untuk berikan yang terbaik.

441
00:39:29,617 --> 00:39:30,618
Hei, Seo Mi-rae.

442
00:39:31,952 --> 00:39:35,247
Awak tahu berapa banyak
jualan coin untuk <i>DYPD </i>dah jatuh?

443
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,041
Apa?

444
00:39:38,209 --> 00:39:40,252
Kontrak Yun Song dah nak tamat.

445
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:43,714
Susahlah nak sambung kontrak
dengan syarat yang memuaskan.

446
00:39:43,798 --> 00:39:46,384
Terpaksalah komiknya tamat musim depan.

447
00:39:47,176 --> 00:39:49,678
Awak kena jaga penulis lain juga.

448
00:39:49,762 --> 00:39:52,014
Tak penatkah ikut telunjuk dia?

449
00:39:52,098 --> 00:39:55,434
Saya akan cakap dengan dia
dan ikhtiarkan sesuatu.

450
00:39:56,018 --> 00:39:59,146
Okey. Macam mana awak nak cakap?

451
00:39:59,897 --> 00:40:00,731
Apa?

452
00:40:03,359 --> 00:40:04,568
Awak pun tak tahu.

453
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:08,989
Hei, awak pun salah, tahu tak?

454
00:40:09,073 --> 00:40:12,993
Kalau penerbit bersungguh-sungguh,
komik itu takkan tenggelam.

455
00:40:13,077 --> 00:40:15,329
Tapi tengoklah apa awak buat!

456
00:40:15,413 --> 00:40:17,081
Dia penulis termahal kita,

457
00:40:17,164 --> 00:40:19,667
tapi baru beberapa bulan, dah huru-hara.

458
00:40:19,750 --> 00:40:21,001
Maaf, bos.

459
00:40:24,839 --> 00:40:25,756
Helo?

460
00:40:33,722 --> 00:40:34,807
Saya tak pasti.

461
00:40:34,890 --> 00:40:37,601
Dia tak mengamuk macam biasa.
Dia diam saja.

462
00:40:41,272 --> 00:40:43,023
Saya datang esoklah.

463
00:40:43,732 --> 00:40:44,817
Pergilah.

464
00:40:45,776 --> 00:40:47,736
Pujukan awak takkan ubah apa-apa.

465
00:40:48,612 --> 00:40:50,364
Lebih baik awak mengamuk.

466
00:40:51,532 --> 00:40:54,076
Saya tahu hari ini akan tiba juga.

467
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,704
Zaman kejatuhan saya.

468
00:40:57,371 --> 00:40:58,873
Dah nasib badan.

469
00:41:01,417 --> 00:41:02,543
Cik Yun.

470
00:41:04,795 --> 00:41:06,338
Saya dah cakap, bukan?

471
00:41:07,381 --> 00:41:10,885
Komik saya laris sebab Choi Si-woo.
Saya manalah ada bakat.

472
00:41:13,304 --> 00:41:15,222
Dah sampai masa saya bersara.

473
00:41:16,265 --> 00:41:19,935
Jual kereta, jual rumah,

474
00:41:20,728 --> 00:41:22,813
jual bangunan.

475
00:41:23,731 --> 00:41:26,567
Apa jual-jual pula?

476
00:41:26,650 --> 00:41:27,485
Cik Yun.

477
00:41:27,568 --> 00:41:30,613
Saya masih nak berjuang untuk <i>DYPD</i>.

478
00:41:30,696 --> 00:41:33,908
Betullah saya sibuk dengan hal peribadi,

479
00:41:33,991 --> 00:41:37,703
jadi maaflah saya tak dapat
fokus betul-betul pada komik awak.

480
00:41:37,786 --> 00:41:39,079
Hal peribadi apa?

481
00:41:40,539 --> 00:41:41,832
Awak curi tulang?

482
00:41:41,916 --> 00:41:44,418
Tak, bukan begitu. Saya…

483
00:41:45,169 --> 00:41:48,506
Mulai sekarang,
saya akan cuba sedaya upaya.

484
00:41:48,589 --> 00:41:51,884
Saya nak awak berusaha juga. Okey?

485
00:41:51,967 --> 00:41:56,639
Saya akan berhempas-pulas
untuk kembalikan <i>DYPD </i>ke nombor satu.

486
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:58,516
Betulkah?

487
00:42:00,142 --> 00:42:03,562
Jomlah kita makan sedap hari ini.

488
00:42:03,646 --> 00:42:04,897
Saya belanja!

489
00:42:05,397 --> 00:42:06,398
Awak belanja?

490
00:42:06,482 --> 00:42:08,150
Saya keluar duit hari ini.

491
00:42:08,651 --> 00:42:10,653
1: PlanC
2: DIA YANG PERLU DIKENAL

492
00:42:10,736 --> 00:42:13,447
Sudah-sudahlah tengok. Awak tak bosankah?

493
00:42:13,531 --> 00:42:17,660
Saya pernah cerita? Dulu En. Cho
sewakan studio untuk saya dan Cik Yun.

494
00:42:17,743 --> 00:42:21,455
Dia letak saya di bawah tanah,
Cik Yun di tingkat atas.

495
00:42:21,539 --> 00:42:26,418
- Dah seratus kali awak cerita.
- Saya dah impikan saat ini sejak itu.

496
00:42:26,502 --> 00:42:27,962
Berilah saya peluang.

497
00:42:28,546 --> 00:42:30,256
Yalah, awak patut gembira.

498
00:42:31,298 --> 00:42:32,800
Tapi kasihan Seo Mi-rae.

499
00:42:34,677 --> 00:42:36,011
Awak rasa dia kecewa?

500
00:42:40,307 --> 00:42:41,392
Saya rasa ya.

501
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:45,396
Aduhai, sejuknya. Kenapa kita datang sini?

502
00:42:45,479 --> 00:42:47,022
Macam mana saya nak balik?

503
00:42:47,106 --> 00:42:50,818
Tak jemukah lepak di kawasan awak saja?
Makanan di sini sedap.

504
00:42:50,901 --> 00:42:52,778
Kedai apa ini? Sejuknya.

505
00:42:53,487 --> 00:42:56,073
Makanlah apa-apa awak nak hari ini!

506
00:42:57,741 --> 00:42:58,909
Itu Park, bukan?

507
00:43:01,954 --> 00:43:03,539
Pergi kedai lainlah.

508
00:43:03,622 --> 00:43:05,666
Cik Yun. Helo.

509
00:43:07,668 --> 00:43:09,628
- Helo.
- Hai.

510
00:43:09,712 --> 00:43:11,046
Helo.

511
00:43:11,130 --> 00:43:14,967
Studio Hwany dekat-dekat sini, bukan?
Kamu raikan kejayaan, ya?

512
00:43:15,050 --> 00:43:17,970
Kami bermesyuarat saja. Kamu pula?

513
00:43:19,013 --> 00:43:21,307
Kami datang untuk tenangkan fikiran.

514
00:43:23,350 --> 00:43:25,269
- Apa khabar?
- Khabar tak baik.

515
00:43:25,352 --> 00:43:27,021
- Baguslah.
- Tak guna.

516
00:43:27,104 --> 00:43:29,898
- Saya kata marilah.
- Okey. Kami pergi dulu.

517
00:43:29,982 --> 00:43:31,191
Budak kurang ajar.

518
00:43:31,275 --> 00:43:33,402
Patutnya kita yang lari dulu.

519
00:43:34,820 --> 00:43:35,988
Cik Yun!

520
00:43:51,754 --> 00:43:53,464
Maaflah, saya terlambat.

521
00:43:53,547 --> 00:43:54,798
Jom tukar kedai.

522
00:43:54,882 --> 00:43:56,884
- Apa? Mana?
- Marilah.

523
00:43:56,967 --> 00:43:58,510
Tunggu!

524
00:44:01,847 --> 00:44:02,765
Tunggu sekejap.

525
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,151
- Biar saya…
- Tak apa, saya nak buat.

526
00:44:17,613 --> 00:44:18,739
Nah, makanlah.

527
00:44:19,281 --> 00:44:21,367
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

528
00:44:21,450 --> 00:44:24,078
Apa masalah dia?

529
00:44:25,954 --> 00:44:28,290
Kita dah nak pergi. Kenapa buka kot?

530
00:44:28,374 --> 00:44:29,625
Semaknya aku tengok.

531
00:44:29,708 --> 00:44:31,418
Kita dah nak pergi?

532
00:44:32,544 --> 00:44:34,129
Saya pergi tandas dulu.

533
00:44:34,213 --> 00:44:35,214
Pergilah.

534
00:44:39,051 --> 00:44:40,636
Cik Yun.

535
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:43,722
Boleh tak jangan kacau suasana?
Awak buat dia cemas!

536
00:44:43,806 --> 00:44:46,684
Jangan cari pasal.
Nanti saya bawa So-yeong pergi.

537
00:44:46,767 --> 00:44:49,812
Eh, dengki betul.
Awak tak boleh buat begitu.

538
00:44:49,895 --> 00:44:52,022
Kenapa tak boleh?

539
00:44:52,106 --> 00:44:55,734
Kalau kami tak pergi,
awak sanggup rehatkan komik awak?

540
00:44:55,818 --> 00:44:57,736
- Rehatkan komik?
- Yalah!

541
00:44:59,988 --> 00:45:01,532
Okey. Ya, saya sanggup…

542
00:45:03,826 --> 00:45:05,285
- Hei.
- Apa?

543
00:45:05,369 --> 00:45:09,790
Janganlah kacau.
Ini rundingan sesama penulis.

544
00:45:10,374 --> 00:45:11,208
Cik Yun.

545
00:45:11,709 --> 00:45:14,670
Saya rela buat apa saja
kalau So-yeong tak pergi.

546
00:45:14,753 --> 00:45:16,630
- Janganlah.
- Awak dengar tak?

547
00:45:17,840 --> 00:45:19,007
Sudah-sudahlah.

548
00:45:19,091 --> 00:45:21,635
Kenapa? Awak kata nak cuba segala cara.

549
00:45:23,971 --> 00:45:25,222
Bila kita nak pergi?

550
00:45:25,305 --> 00:45:26,849
Apa? Tak jadilah.

551
00:45:27,683 --> 00:45:28,684
Apa?

552
00:45:28,767 --> 00:45:30,853
Makanan di sini sedap. Makanlah.

553
00:45:30,936 --> 00:45:33,564
- Panas. Bukalah kot.
- Ya.

554
00:45:34,064 --> 00:45:35,357
Nak laga gelas?

555
00:45:35,441 --> 00:45:36,984
- Ya!
- Okey.

556
00:45:38,193 --> 00:45:39,027
Sedapnya.

557
00:45:39,111 --> 00:45:41,155
- Minum!
- Minum!

558
00:45:41,655 --> 00:45:43,115
Aduhai.

559
00:45:50,038 --> 00:45:52,750
Dah. Jom parti.

560
00:45:53,250 --> 00:45:55,335
Ya, minum puas-puas.

561
00:45:55,419 --> 00:45:56,545
- Minum!
- Minum!

562
00:46:01,258 --> 00:46:03,010
Minum susu pagi-pagi…

563
00:46:03,093 --> 00:46:03,927
Susu!

564
00:46:04,428 --> 00:46:05,345
Dia minum susu.

565
00:46:06,722 --> 00:46:07,556
Betulkah?

566
00:46:08,515 --> 00:46:10,434
<i>Jatuh hati…</i>

567
00:46:10,517 --> 00:46:13,937
Mara! Serbu pertahanan musuh!

568
00:46:14,021 --> 00:46:15,355
Kita dah sampai.

569
00:46:18,025 --> 00:46:20,194
<i>…bererti mencari alasan…</i>

570
00:46:23,572 --> 00:46:24,573
Ya?

571
00:46:25,157 --> 00:46:28,494
Awak nak pinjam?
Pulangkanlah bila-bila nanti.

572
00:46:28,577 --> 00:46:30,829
- Kalau awak tak kisah…
- Ambillah.

573
00:46:30,913 --> 00:46:33,415
<i>…untuk luangkan lebih banyak masa bersama.</i>

574
00:46:33,499 --> 00:46:37,085
So-yeong, Krismas ini…

575
00:46:38,545 --> 00:46:39,922
Kris…

576
00:46:43,842 --> 00:46:45,719
Krismas nanti, awak buat apa?

577
00:46:45,803 --> 00:46:48,931
Tonton anime dan filem di rumah.

578
00:46:49,014 --> 00:46:50,098
Kalau begitu…

579
00:46:50,182 --> 00:46:51,600
Aduhai, zaman sekarang,

580
00:46:51,683 --> 00:46:54,853
hidup budak muda lebih bosan
daripada hidup kita.

581
00:46:54,937 --> 00:46:57,523
Seronok sangatkah hidup awak?

582
00:46:57,606 --> 00:46:59,191
Cuti nanti awak buat apa?

583
00:46:59,274 --> 00:47:01,985
Saya dah cakap
saya ada teman lelaki, bukan?

584
00:47:02,069 --> 00:47:03,737
Saya dah cakaplah.

585
00:47:03,821 --> 00:47:05,489
Betul. Awak dah cakap.

586
00:47:05,572 --> 00:47:07,241
Awak tak percaya?

587
00:47:07,324 --> 00:47:09,743
Seo dah cakap dengan dia dalam telefon.

588
00:47:09,827 --> 00:47:11,620
- Betul tak?
- Ya.

589
00:47:12,538 --> 00:47:13,372
Betulkah?

590
00:47:14,081 --> 00:47:14,915
Betul.

591
00:47:15,457 --> 00:47:17,209
Dia sayang betul Cik Yun.

592
00:47:18,877 --> 00:47:22,631
Bila masa pula kamu jumpa?
Asyik sibuk kerja saja.

593
00:47:22,714 --> 00:47:23,549
Apa?

594
00:47:24,633 --> 00:47:25,717
Saya…

595
00:47:26,218 --> 00:47:29,054
Saya curi-curi masa kalau sempat.

596
00:47:29,555 --> 00:47:33,350
Saya sajakah di sini yang sedang bercinta?

597
00:47:33,976 --> 00:47:37,396
Apa kena dengan kamu semua?
Muda-mudalah patut bercinta.

598
00:47:37,479 --> 00:47:39,064
Apa-apalah.

599
00:47:39,731 --> 00:47:41,650
Saya cemburu betul.

600
00:47:42,442 --> 00:47:44,862
Saya nak makan snek lagi.

601
00:47:48,323 --> 00:47:50,659
<i>Alamak. Aku lupa.</i>

602
00:47:51,952 --> 00:47:53,453
Snek dah habis.

603
00:47:55,622 --> 00:47:57,624
Arak pun dah habis.

604
00:47:58,375 --> 00:48:00,043
Pergi beli arak lagi.

605
00:48:20,147 --> 00:48:21,982
Saya…

606
00:48:24,651 --> 00:48:26,486
Maaflah sebab tipu awak.

607
00:48:28,280 --> 00:48:29,615
Tipu apa?

608
00:48:31,241 --> 00:48:32,075
Saya…

609
00:48:32,993 --> 00:48:36,246
Saya beritahu awak
yang saya ada teman lelaki.

610
00:48:39,833 --> 00:48:42,836
Saya tak berniat nak tipu awak,

611
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:47,257
tapi saya tak pernah alami situasi itu,
jadi saya gelabah sikit.

612
00:48:51,428 --> 00:48:52,346
Maafkan saya juga.

613
00:48:54,598 --> 00:48:55,432
Apa?

614
00:48:56,850 --> 00:49:00,562
Saya patut dah agak awak tak selesa
kalau saya luahkan perasaan,

615
00:49:01,271 --> 00:49:02,606
tapi saya pentingkan diri.

616
00:49:09,279 --> 00:49:11,365
Terima kasih sebab cakap begitu.

617
00:49:12,532 --> 00:49:15,702
Sebenarnya, baru-baru ini,
saya asyik terfikir tentangnya.

618
00:49:16,370 --> 00:49:17,245
Sebab

619
00:49:17,913 --> 00:49:21,625
awak kata awak terkilan
sebelum kita bertolak ke Busan.

620
00:49:24,169 --> 00:49:25,504
Saya dah tak terkilan.

621
00:49:29,299 --> 00:49:30,175
Betulkah?

622
00:49:32,552 --> 00:49:33,720
Baguslah.

623
00:49:39,643 --> 00:49:40,811
Seo Mi-rae.

624
00:49:42,854 --> 00:49:43,689
Ya?

625
00:49:46,108 --> 00:49:46,942
Sekarang…

626
00:49:49,528 --> 00:49:52,030
betulkah awak tak ada teman lelaki?

627
00:49:57,995 --> 00:49:59,830
Awak tak kisah saya tahu?

628
00:50:03,208 --> 00:50:04,710
Ya, rasanya.

629
00:50:10,173 --> 00:50:11,091
Mulai sekarang…

630
00:50:18,765 --> 00:50:20,517
boleh saya ikut kata hati?

631
00:50:43,415 --> 00:50:46,084
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

632
00:53:44,554 --> 00:53:46,264
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

